4.00	Phillip_R._Ford	Phillip R. Ford	Phillip Raymond Ford (born May 31, 1961 in San Rafael, California) is a stage and film producer, director and entertainer who served most of the 1980s as "honorary straight man" in the legendary San Francisco drag troupe Sluts A-Go-Go. He is best known as the producer and director of Vegas in Space, the celebrated cult film starring the Sluts A-Go-Go, which created a sensation at the 1992 Sundance Film Festival, appeared at festivals worldwide, was broadcast on USA Network's Up All Night with Rhonda Shear and was featured on Entertainment Tonight and the E! Entertainment Television Network.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/28/FordWiki.jpg/220px-FordWiki.jpg
